lot.description_en: The image shows a modern bathroom with dark and light gray tiles. There's a glass-enclosed shower on the right, featuring a rainfall showerhead. A white vanity with a sleek black-framed mirror is centered on the back wall. A washing machine is placed on the left, partially under a counter with white cabinet fronts. The floor is a shiny gray, complemented by recessed ceiling lights. A small green mat is in front of the shower, and a white sink and toilet complete the setup, offering a clean, contemporary look.

There are visible pipes near the sink area, hinting at basic plumbing.

Image batumi_arendaaaa/2025/06/fd6008c3d4a19c21bbdf565225c1962000931d9abca5907b47042a719f0d5330.jpg:
The image shows a spacious dining room with a classic, rustic vibe. The room features a large oval wooden dining table surrounded by six intricately carved chairs. A decorative chandelier hangs above the table, providing warm lighting. The walls are painted yellow, enhancing the cozy atmosphere. Along one side of the room is a large wooden cabinet with glass doors for displaying items. The floor is made of wooden planks. Additionally, there is a square heater placed against the wall, and sheer curtains hanging on the windows. The ceiling has decorative crown molding.

Image batumi_arendaaaa/2025/06/460d1977d220199eabe9d8e06f20a47b3e341c2b8df92a7e8253e9b832419be5.jpg:
The image depicts a bathroom with dark marbled tiles on the walls and floor. It features a white bathtub with a handheld showerhead, a bidet, and a sink with a mirror above it. There is a bottle of liquid soap on the sink. The ceiling has a light fixture and vent. The bathroom gives a modern, polished vibe with a focus on functionality.

Image batumi_arendaaaa/2025/06/a672b34504a98c71ed2d9353330938b525d69b6bd631027ac15b208265bd376b.jpg:
This image shows a narrow laundry or utility area with tiled flooring. There is a washing machine located at the end of the space, alongside a metal drying rack. An ironing board with a colorful cover is set up next to the wall. The room has several windows with blinds, allowing natural light to filter in. The ceiling features recessed lighting, and the walls are painted a light beige color. A door with a silver handle leads to the rest of the apartment. The space has a clean, functional appearance.

Image batumi_arendaaaa/2025/06/05fa87c5573261f3823d760594c158f78fc95b2356b7bdba687c1a4c42a1e7f8.jpg:
The image shows a partially enclosed balcony with tiled flooring, offering a view of nearby buildings and trees. The structures in the background suggest a mix of mid-rise residential and office buildings, with some greenery visible. The balcony is open on one side with a railing, and there is a small, square window on the right wall providing additional light. The sky appears overcast, indicating cloudy weather. The overall vibe of the balcony is simple and functional, typical of residential apartments. The area seems relatively elevated, possibly on a middle floor.

The image shows a collage of four different manicures. 

1. The top left features nails with a natural, glossy finish in a soft, nude shade.
2. The top right displays nails in a shimmery, light green polish.
3. The bottom left presents nails with a polished, pastel pink color with a glossy finish, featuring an almond shape.
4. The bottom right shows a set of nails in a glossy pastel pink, also with an almond shape adorned with several gold rings.

Each manicure emphasizes a neat and tidy appearance.

The plant has strikingly elongated leaves with a mix of dark green, deep purple, and light green stripes, creating a visually appealing contrast. The leaves are smooth and glossy, indicating health. The soil in the small pot appears dark, suggesting it is well-watered.

Image baraholka_ge/2025/06/3fa826769397710561edfe6b150f5436fad5965f5e9e0ecb0213a19d26a70db6.jpg:
The image shows an electric kettle with a glass body and a black plastic handle. The kettle has markings for 0.5 L, 1.0 L, and 1.5 L on the side to indicate water levels. It features a stainless steel base, which gives it a modern look. The kettle is positioned on a dark surface, which seems to be a kitchen counter. A power cord with a plug is visible, indicating it is ready for use. The background consists of white tiles with a marble pattern, adding a sleek aesthetic to the kitchen. Overall, the kettle appears clean and new.

Image baraholka_ge/2025/06/6445a63536fb2cd47b6bd2eb5c5d8354318f94d4731fc23c19e8f0fa1721997d.jpg:
The image shows a KUMTEL brand tabletop oven with a glossy black and red finish. The oven features a transparent glass door, allowing visibility of its interior. Inside, there is a wire rack for placing food items. 

The control panel on the right side includes three knobs: one for temperature setting, another for timer control, and the third possibly for adjusting cooking functions. The oven has indicators lit up on the panel. It is placed on a white circular table. The background is a light-colored wall, and the overall ambiance appears modern and clean. There are no visible stains or damages on the appliance. No additional items are shown in the image.

Image baraholka_ge/2025/06/ce73b17ba9e46883e07664897a06a852fe41ef4dbbb89d16c58fc95018c38c40.jpg:
The image shows a black Xiaomi Wi-Fi router. It features two upright antennas extending from the top, and the router's body has a simple and sleek design with the "mi" logo prominently displayed on the front. Below the router, there is an open box, likely the packaging, which contains additional information such as product specifications or instructions. The surface appears smooth and light, likely a table or desk. The overall vibe is modern and minimalistic.

Image baraholka_ge/2025/06/b65f3c7a9fdf1ff0eb518185bfa481c384781c309acc53f4af11c6b4fe49686c.jpg:
The image features a small kitchen appliance set by Arzum, labeled "Blanco Mini." It includes a handheld mixer with a white body and three attachments: a pair of beaters, a blending stick, and a food chopper container. The chopper has a transparent plastic bowl, while the blending stick has a metallic finish. The appliance is plugged in, with visible power buttons. The items are arranged on a plain white surface, and there is a box in the background with product information. The overall vibe is modern and sleek, suitable for contemporary kitchens.

lots.title_en: Studio on Shartava 10, 31st floor with sea view
lots.description_en: Cozy studio for short-term rent in New Wave, Shartava 10, with a designer renovation. Stunning views from the balcony and panoramic windows on the 31st floor overlooking the city, mountains, and sea! Located in an area with developed infrastructure: shops within walking distance, the sea is a 10-minute walk away, near the boulevard, a pond with singing fountains, and Heroes Alley. The apartment includes air conditioning, refrigerator, electric stove, and washing machine with drying. Pets are negotiable.

The room features a stylish and modern interior with a large bed against a decorative wall with sconces on each side. It has a tufted headboard and gray bedding. There are two side tables flanking the bed. The floor is light-colored wood or laminate, complementing the soft pink and white walls.

A chandelier and decorative ceiling medallion add elegance. Floor-to-ceiling windows provide a city view, possibly from a high floor, and there is a small glass desk with a chair near the window. A full-length mirror rests against the wall. A white dresser with a few decorative items sits opposite the bed. The room also includes air conditioning.

Image batumiarendachat/2025/06/b95319a96329e16c91b341e408999c6a257ba02d29a35bed45eaea65f26983cd.jpg:
The image shows a spacious, elegantly designed bedroom with a mix of classical and modern elements. The room has light wood flooring and pink-accented walls. A large bed with a gray, tufted headboard is centrally placed, covered with a matching quilt and complemented by neatly folded towels on top. There are two bedside tables with decorative wall sconces above them. 

A ceiling chandelier adds a touch of classic style to the room. Along one wall, there is a built-in cabinet with glass doors displaying a kettle and various items. A small dining chair is visible in the corner, adding functionality to the room. The overall vibe is bright and sophisticated, with a mixture of soft color tones and ornate detailing. A large window suggests a high floor, given the angle of the view.

Image batumiarendachat/2025/06/43db6bc4b7ae839d1b53fce92d4217999345178a06966eb263381870588dd140.jpg:
The image shows an elegantly styled hallway with light pink walls and white furniture. There is a white dresser with three drawers, decorated with a lamp that has a textured base and a white shade. Beside it is a small round table. On the wall, there's a large mirror and a framed picture. The floor is covered with light-colored wood or laminate. In the background, there's a tall white wardrobe with mirrored doors, and the entrance door has a rustic, weathered look. The space exudes a cozy, classic ambiance.

Image batumiarendachat/2025/06/59f3ee4993c31f51de528752c4faccef53f70ff1088fc4da9db8ea59a8bb1d92.jpg:
This elegant room features a chic corner with a white ornamental fireplace and a stylish decorative piece on top. A large, ornate framed mirror leans against the wall. The space also includes two high stools at a counter or narrow table, positioned by a window with a stunning cityscape and sea view, suggesting it's on a high floor. The room has a modern design with parquet flooring, dark curtains, and a subtle, neutral color palette. A small chandelier adds a touch of sophistication, and there's a wall-mounted air conditioning unit for climate control.

Image batumiarendachat/2025/06/292971bb8e630740fda78382da093fbf1ab8d48169105d7d00f2aa36f8c3abae.jpg:
The image shows a modern apartment interior with a view of the city. A small dining area is set by floor-to-ceiling windows, offering a view of high-rise buildings and a distant seascape. The dining set includes a tall table and two chairs. The room features a bed with a grey patterned bedspread, and there is an air conditioning unit above the window. The balcony is visible, furnished with two bar-height chairs. The scene is well-lit with natural sunlight, creating a cozy atmosphere.

Image batumiarendachat/2025/06/26af10e057f254050b511b3fcf40a984636691c81e153b860dd56bced68e8cca.jpg:
The image shows a stylish interior corner with an ornate white mantelpiece featuring intricate floral carvings. On top of the mantel are decorative items, including a textured sculpture, a transparent vase, and a cylindrical container. Above the mantel hangs a textured artwork. To the side, part of a large mirror with a detailed frame is visible. A small bar table with two high chairs is near the window, offering a view of high-rise buildings and mountains. The floor is light wood, and heavy dark curtains frame the window, contributing to the modern and elegant ambiance. The room appears to be on a high floor, given the elevated city view.

Image batumiarendachat/2025/06/98511633829a08b0766f762feb758125486681cb490bd26701431a8b54f42bef.jpg:
The bathroom features ornate, gray, patterned tiles on the floor and walls, creating a cohesive design. A glass-enclosed shower with a modern chrome fixture is positioned on one side. There's a towel rack above the washing machine, which is a Gorenje model. Wall-mounted amenities include a small shelf, holding toiletries. The overall vibe is modern with a touch of elegance due to the detailed tile pattern. A toilet is situated next to the washing machine, and a soft-colored mat is placed in front of the shower.

Image batumiarendachat/2025/06/c03df30de2ca9e1fee8d374e3acde503de6f7598b8cf353f034568770bafd7b7.jpg:
The image shows a kitchen area with a modern design. It features a set of white cabinets with glass-paneled doors on the upper half and solid doors below. The countertop holds a black electric kettle next to a sink with a faucet. The backsplash is tiled with a subtle pattern. The walls are painted a muted pink color, which extends to the ceiling molding. The flooring appears to be a light wood laminate. A small open closet is visible in the corner, and part of a bed is in the foreground, suggesting the space might be a studio apartment. There's no gas boiler visible. The overall vibe is clean and contemporary.

Image batumiarendachat/2025/06/5982f49da46d260a54cfe212f7aa7476f0a2643fdc5ff95d20ad089c3e0f0c39.jpg:
The image shows a modern high-rise building, part of a cluster of similar skyscrapers. The facade is primarily made of glass, giving it a sleek and contemporary appearance. The building has a distinctive curved design, and there's a sign at the entrance that reads "NEW WAVE". Palm trees and well-maintained landscaping are visible in the foreground, enhancing the urban setting. The surrounding buildings also feature glass exteriors, contributing to the modern skyline. The sky is clear, indicating a sunny day.

Image baraholka_batumi_home/2025/06/ed4230b676a01b541fb16e55f973094ca4ecacfebcd1d20cc6b2af721da2d4fe.jpg:
This image shows a floral dress with a dark background and a vibrant rose pattern in shades of red and pink with green leaves. The dress has long sleeves and a ruffled hem. Accompanying the dress is a thin, brown belt placed beside it. The items are laid out on a light wooden floor, highlighting the contrasting colors and intricate design of the fabric. The style is feminine and could be suitable for both casual and semi-formal occasions.

Image baraholka_batumi_home/2025/06/1b61aa788438a436a3610c11a6af8b48cccd03881846e80be03fdb3d3b580bc3.jpg:
The image shows a pair of light blue denim jeans laid out on a wooden floor. The jeans have a worn and distressed look, with frayed hems at the bottom. They feature standard elements like front pockets, belt loops, and a button closure. The overall appearance is casual and slightly vintage.

Image baraholka_batumi_home/2025/06/8254b030837a6b8a8786ae2d79111563a54c66ccf5812b5b84de528dbd9099aa.jpg:
The image features a black crew neck sweatshirt laid out on a wooden floor. The sweatshirt has a simple, classic design with long sleeves and ribbed cuffs and hem. The fabric appears soft and comfortable, suitable for casual wear. No additional features such as logos or patterns are visible.

Image baraholka_batumi_home/2025/06/e0ece51aad5d1dc230cd931691801e88a57542c5ff18b668021e4525857fa38a.jpg:
The image shows a bright red blouse laid out on a light wood surface. The blouse features a button-up front with buttons that match the fabric color. It has long sleeves with a loose, billowy design, and a collar that stands upright. The material appears lightweight and flowy, creating a relaxed and stylish look. The wooden flooring underneath adds a subtle, natural backdrop to the vibrant garment.

Image baraholka_batumi_home/2025/06/256f98adfae739830b4df1042701e3e00efe1ef5b5b070d9e5c06e7e23c3c203.jpg:
These are light gray shorts made from a soft, slightly crinkled fabric. The shorts feature a drawstring with metal eyelets on the waistband, alongside belt loops for added versatility. There are side pockets on both sides, and they appear to be knee-length. The shorts are laid out on a wooden floor.

Image baraholka_batumi_home/2025/06/1dbca3f60b5defc4b7d0af1fc1dbbee5d602b7af9b5f76bb6fd2df1aaf772fe7.jpg:
This image shows a vibrant, long-sleeved floral dress spread out on a wooden floor. The dress is predominantly red, adorned with small white, blue, and black floral patterns. It features long sleeves and a flowing, lightweight fabric with a partial inner lining that is visible beneath the lifted section of the skirt. The design suggests a relaxed, yet elegant style, suitable for both casual and semi-formal occasions. The wood flooring adds a warm, natural backdrop to the scene.

lot.description_en: Hello. My name is Nikolai. I provide qualified services for the electrification of residential, commercial, and industrial facilities in compliance with all current standards and requirements. Electrical installation work according to regulations - professionally, from scratch and turnkey, without intermediaries! Specialization: Design and installation of power supply according to the requirements of PUE, SNiP 3.05.06-85, GOST R 50571 and IEC 60364. Performing electrical installation of any complexity - from initial wiring to commissioning. Assembly, configuration, and labeling of distribution boards (standard and individual schemes). Installation of circuit breakers, RCDs, differential automata, voltage control relays, and other modular automation. Installation of smart home systems. Mandatory soldering of connections using quality solder and flux - durability, absence of contact resistance. Replacement of aluminum wiring with copper, calculation of cable cross-section by load and line length. Indoor and outdoor lighting, grounding, lightning protection. Checking insulation resistance, testing the grounding circuit, and preparing protocols. Principles of work: I work according to approved schemes, strictly within the framework of regulations and project documentation. I use cable and wire products with certificates of compliance. I take into account selectivity, load balancing, and power reserve. All installation work is carried out carefully, with minimal interference in the finish. I provide guarantees, test protocols, and technical documentation upon completion of work. Additionally: Free consultation and site visit (within Batumi and nearby areas). Support at all stages - from purchasing equipment and materials to final testing. Preparation of a preliminary estimate.

The image shows a coastal city view from a high floor, likely above the tenth level. In the foreground, there's a road running parallel to the sea, with a visible water park featuring slides and pools. The sea stretches out in the background under a cloudy sky. On the left, there are several high-rise buildings with a mix of traditional and modern architecture. Cars are parked along the street and in a parking lot, adding to the urban feel. The overall atmosphere is bustling, with a balance of leisure and residential elements.

Image arenda_batumi/2025/06/8fb3821b7c3a3cc1c431cec6111578f4fd02530b19c76e818a9ebb34b1cb2bb2.jpg:
This image shows a compact, modern studio apartment. The room features a bed with white linens and a dark blue throw, positioned against a wall with a framed abstract map. Next to the bed is a vertical wooden slat partition dividing the sleeping area from the kitchen. The kitchen has white cabinets, a washing machine, a small counter with a microwave, and a blue-tiled backsplash. The flooring is wood, and there's an industrial-style hanging light fixture. A small dining table with a chair is adjacent to the kitchen area. The apartment has a contemporary and functional design.

Image arenda_batumi/2025/06/0b9d0641931f8c73e67ce5bf5533948e688ef52df537922fa1f53393699ac55e.jpg:
This image shows a modern studio apartment with a cozy layout. To the left, there are white built-in closets for ample storage. The room features a dark-colored couch facing towards a bed, placed near large windows with both sheer and dark curtains. The flooring is warm-toned wood, adding to the elegant ambiance. A contemporary light fixture hangs from the ceiling. Close to the entrance, there is a small kitchenette with a wooden partition wall and illuminated by pendant lighting. A door on the right leads to another space, possibly a bathroom. The overall design is sleek and functional.

Image arenda_batumi/2025/06/0e28a133f40eb409912000339eef6abb099d86f5b4a0790cd68a920459b2f2ff.jpg:

On the wall, there is a small mounted television above a wooden desk, accompanied by a black chair. A small refrigerator sits nearby. The room is accented by blue curtains and a piece of blue abstract art. A modern ceiling light fixture adds character to the space. The room has a clean and contemporary feel.

Image arenda_batumi/2025/06/e5cb507474d4c0becaa326718c157bd2393e7948f42feb1d1d311bf0b722dc77.jpg:
The image shows a modern bathroom featuring a glass-enclosed shower area with a chrome shower head and wall-mounted caddy holding toiletries. The walls are tiled with beige and cream mosaic tiles, creating a warm aesthetic. A white towel is neatly hung on a metal towel rack above a mid-sized washbasin with a chrome faucet. Next to the mirror above the sink is a wooden shelf. The sink appears to be set in a dark-toned cabinet. Recessed lighting in the ceiling provides illumination, and there's a small waste bin on the floor.

The space is well-utilized, combining functionality with modern aesthetics.

The image shows a compact bathroom with a modern design. It features a white pedestal sink and a wall-mounted mirror with glass shelves. The toilet is positioned beside the sink.
